reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a drawer similar to the Alex drawers for less money and this was it ! This an easy drawer set to put together took about the exact 80 min predicted to put it together as a whole. The inside drawer screws that connect to the railings that help pull the drawers out were hard to align and get in it took quite a few tries but they went in. Overall love the drawers hold quite a bit and are a smooth pull out and push in would defined order a second one!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 14, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I wish I could give zero stars. Nice cabinet easy to assemble just takes a lot of time. My issue is the horrible odor that you cannot get rid of in the drawers. I have tried everything including vinegar.,ZORBX, OZIUM and even gone as far as caulking and painting the drawers thinking it would seal the odor in. No use the odor is still there! It smells like something crawled in and died in the cabinet. I called Amazon and it’s outside the return window they cannot help me. I have to contact the seller. I think this is $149 just wasted because I cannot keep this in my house and I don’t have faith that the seller is going to help me. I will be so careful with purchases of this kind in the future from Amazon.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better than expected
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this with two other units of varying sizes and shapes. This was far better than the natural wood unit that I purchased. The hardware was durable and so much easier to put together. It didn’t take me long at all. Just a tip, start installing the drawers from the bottom up, it makes it easier to see what you’re doing while putting it together. The back of the unit is not pretty, but I have it against a wall so it suits my needs perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Drawers are not even 12” deep
reviews.reviewText: It is a solid piece, lots of wood. However, my problem is that the interior drawer measurements are not as listed. It says they are 13+in deep, but they are closer to 11” inside. I figured I was not careful reading and it was actually saying the depth from the front of the outside to the back of the outside, but that doesn’t even really reach 13 inches either. I’m just annoyed bc I searched high and low to find one that would have tall enough drawers to fit something specific, now they’re not deep enough.
